<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1909/518699-625x417.jpg" alt="Brand South Africa is set to host its fourth annual Nation Brand Forum" width="625" height="417">The Nation Brand Forum is one of Brand South Africa’s flagship programmes that affords active participation of all stakeholders in achieving a coherent and compelling Nation Brand image, reputation and identity. Under the theme; ‘Reviving South Africa’s Nation Brand identity and narrative’. The Nation Brand Forum is set to be hosted on the 10th October 2019.<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1909/518703-625x417.jpg" alt="Brand South Africa is set to host its fourth annual Nation Brand Forum" width="625" height="417">For more information, visit www.brandsouthafrica.com and follow the conversation @Brand_SA #NationBrandForum19To see highlights of the 2018 Nation Brand Forum click here.<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1909/518704-625x949.jpg" alt="Brand South Africa is set to host its fourth annual Nation Brand Forum" width="625" height="949">